From 694d9b0aae25f136a5883c52001240483471caf5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ripan Deuri <quic_rdeuri@quicinc.com>
Date: Fri, 28 Mar 2025 18:59:30 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] wifi: ath12k: ieee80211_ops Tx callback for wifi7

The current code splits the Tx functionality between common and
architecture-specific modules. Define the ieee80211_ops Tx callback in
the architecture-specific module to avoid additional indirections caused
by the common Tx function calling the architecture-specific Tx functions
via ops.

Signed-off-by: Ripan Deuri <quic_rdeuri@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
